---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Fabric Technology | Yilong Medical Scrubs - OEKO-TEX Certified"
  description="Yilong three-tier fabric system: Premium 205 GSM, Standard 180 GSM, Lightweight 130 GSM. OEKO-TEX certified. SGS tested antibacterial greater than 99.9 percent, waterproof 15.0 mbar. ISO 9001/14001/45001 certified manufacturer."
  keywords="medical scrubs fabric, 4-way stretch hospital uniform, SGS antibacterial scrubs, OEKO-TEX fabric, SGS waterproof medical uniform"
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 text-secondary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">
      Core Technology
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">Fabric Technology</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Three decades of fabric formula refinement. Three performance tiers. OEKO-TEX certified. SGS tested antibacterial and waterproof options.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Fabric Comparison Table -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 text-slate-900">Built for Healthcare. Tested by Time.</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Three fabric tiers engineered for different global markets. All certified, all tested, all backed by 30 years of manufacturing expertise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <table class="w-full text-sm md:text-base min-w-[700px]">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-slate-900 text-white">
            <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Fabric Tier</th>
            <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Composition</th>
            <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Weight</th>
            <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Feel</th>
            <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Best For</th>
            <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Price</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
          <tr class="bg-slate-50">
            <td class="py-4 px-5 font-black text-secondary">Premium Series</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">72% Polyester / 21% Rayon / 7% Spandex</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5 font-bold">205 GSM</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Ultra-soft, silky drape</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">USA / Canada D2C brands</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">$$$</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 px-5 font-black text-secondary">Standard Series</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Polyester / Spandex blend</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5 font-bold">180 GSM</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Comfortable, durable</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Hospital groups, distributors</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">$$</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-slate-50">
            <td class="py-4 px-5 font-black text-secondary">Lightweight Series</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Polyester / Spandex blend</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5 font-bold">130 GSM</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Lightweight, breathable</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">Philippines, ME, Africa, LATAM</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-5">$</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-xs text-slate-400">
      P = Polyester (durability) . R = Rayon (softness, moisture absorption) . SP = Spandex (4-way stretch)
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Trust Badges Strip - with OEKO-TEX(R) -->
<section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-8">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 md:gap-10 text-center">
      <div>
        <div class="text-secondary font-black text-lg">OEKO-TEX(R)</div>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Standard 100</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px bg-slate-700"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-secondary font-black text-lg">ISO 9001:2015</div>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Quality Management</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px bg-slate-700"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-secondary font-black text-lg">ISO 14001:2015</div>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Environmental</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px bg-slate-700"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-secondary font-black text-lg">ISO 45001:2018</div>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Occupational Safety</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px bg-slate-700"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-secondary font-black text-lg">SGS</div>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Factory Verified</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px bg-slate-700"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-secondary font-black text-lg">100%</div>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Pre-Ship QC</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OEKO-TEX + SGS Wash Data -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- OEKO-TEX with green check icon -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-2xl font-black">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-green-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Certified</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 text-slate-900">OEKO-TEX Standard 100</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            All Yilong fabrics are OEKO-TEX Standard 100 certified. Every batch independently tested by OEKO-TEX authorized laboratories for harmful substances. Safe for prolonged skin contact in high-sweat healthcare environments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wash Test -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 border border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900 mb-6">Wash Durability - SGS Verified</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">20x</div>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">After 20 Machine Washes</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> No deformation or shrinkage</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> Color fastness: Grade 4 to 5 / 5</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> 4-way stretch recovery: greater than 95%</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> No pilling visible</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> Shrinkage: less than 0.5%</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">40x</div>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">After 40 Machine Washes</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> Fabric strength retention: greater than 90%</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> No significant color fading</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> Seam integrity maintained</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black mt-0.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span> Elastic recovery: greater than 85%</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-6">* SGS tested on Premium 205 GSM fabric. Full test report available upon request with bulk order.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Functional Fabric Options: SGS Antibacterial and Waterproof (with emoji) -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">SGS Lab Verified</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-slate-900">Functional Fabric Treatments</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500">These are not marketing claims. These are SGS test results you can verify.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- SGS Antibacterial with emoji -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-green-300 shadow-md relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-500 text-white text-[10px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl">SGS VERIFIED</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">&#128104;&#127808;</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Antibacterial Treatment</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-green-600 font-bold">SGS tested per AATCC 100-2019</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-5 border border-green-100">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Tested against three pathogens:</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-slate-700">E. coli, S. aureus, C. albicans</span>
                <span class="font-black text-green-600">greater than 99.9% reduction</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Silver ion antibacterial treatment inhibits bacterial growth on fabric surface. Reduces cross-contamination risk in clinical environments. Ideal for ER, ICU, surgery, and high-infection-risk units.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Available on all fabric tiers - Min. 200 sets</p>
        </div>

        <!-- SGS Waterproof with emoji -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-blue-300 shadow-md relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-500 text-white text-[10px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl">SGS TESTED</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">&#128167;</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Waterproof Treatment</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-bold">SGS tested per AATCC TM127</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-5 border border-blue-100">
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-slate-700">Hydrostatic head resistance</span>
                <span class="font-black text-blue-600">15.0 mbar</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-slate-700">Classification</span>
                <span class="font-black text-blue-600">Water resistant</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">DWR (Durable Water Repellent) treatment repels fluids and liquids. Resists daily liquid spills and stains in clinical settings. Essential for surgery, emergency, and neonatal units.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Available on all fabric tiers - Min. 200 sets</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Moisture Wicking with emoji -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">&#127783;</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Moisture-Wicking</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold">Built-in fabric property</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Enhanced moisture transport moves sweat away from skin to fabric surface for rapid evaporation. Critical for hot climates, long shifts, and high-activity healthcare roles.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Available on all fabric tiers - Min. 100 sets</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Anti-Wrinkle with emoji -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">&#128135;</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Anti-Wrinkle Treatment</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold">Factory-applied finish</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Reduces fabric wrinkling after washing for a consistently neat appearance. Ideal for environments where professional presentation is paramount throughout the workday.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Available on all fabric tiers - Min. 100 sets</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">Functional treatments require minimum order quantities. SGS test reports available upon request.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-secondary text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-700 transition shadow-md">Request SGS Test Reports and Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 4-Way Stretch -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 text-slate-900">What is 4-Way Stretch?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        4-way stretch means the fabric stretches in both directions - lengthwise and crosswise - providing maximum freedom of movement. Healthcare professionals bend, lift, reach, and crouch throughout long shifts. Yilong 4-way stretch scrubs move with the body, reducing fatigue and increasing comfort.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-2xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">Up/Down</div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Vertical Stretch</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-2xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">Left/Right</div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Horizontal Stretch</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="text-2xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">Snap Back</div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Instant Recovery</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-slate-900 text-white text-center">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-4">Have Questions About Our Fabrics?</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-6">Request fabric swatches, SGS test reports, or talk to our technical team. We will help you choose the right fabric for your target market.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-secondary text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-700 transition shadow-lg">Request Swatches and SGS Test Reports</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
